ButtercupReader Swedish
------------------------
This is NOT the official ButtercupReader. The official version created by Andrew Tokeley and team can be found at http://www.buttercupreader.net/.

This version intends to adapt ButtercupReader for Bliss users, and provide a Swedish localized version.


Dependencies
------------

For Visual Studio 2008
======================
Microsoft Visual Studio 2008 Service Pack 1
http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/details.aspx?FamilyId=FBEE1648-7106-44A7-9649-6D9F6D58056E&displaylang=en

Microsoft Silverlight 3 Tools for Visual Studio 2008 SP1
http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/details.aspx?familyid=9442b0f2-7465-417a-88f3-5e7b5409e9dd&displaylang=en

Silverlight 3 Toolkit November 2009
http://silverlight.codeplex.com/releases/view/36060


Logging
=======
Turn on logging in Buttercup.htm by appending &log=true to the url
Look at the log file by the name buttercup.log in a subdirectory of 
%AppData%/LocalLow/Microsoft/Silverlight